MD3a9QXWcPiXPqbiZrpp1zNWPMyScJKlLEEgxX8IT88y5-IOo8dzNp4PIk38523ngAndZ899HrhIv3XfXwVOPbqLcujpbjSEvTLRBLWTyl0Rtv4Y6xTdgjt1qKV2ZYfyDwE9INu8pp2seglkA_3-zEMnsNmymhQCTEMhdXTTKakbx8em9ANtVCTNE-tNBlcLEp6ff5mT_VKAsyFcg/YQnYfLpOGwgmtCQfEAzJxoAPrfsO8JuD/7" target="_blank"&gt;脱钩&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;阅读有关唐纳德·特朗普总统如何在数十个国家的互惠征税中暂停按钮的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/-UN8nIvi99LaGM7_c8TVgyKSPSd_xaIvDAIgImeKYAfWIa_8yASqWRFP0n5i6GQuv1Ba-HgpE0Xdcnog85UpV45hoR1jmOcFKbI4vhKTq3_H3RpSzJeE-dz61aLS_yPWpEdaFGH2CvFlgsxm4lBU0jFOHqf-TkSRZYrU0-75CexuewJK-7dAEHbKOFOSW63f5FPokyTFAOEJ_9XLX3XX7wpc7MCa6zkBUvht-LBnNHcsfT_Kk-UdiqY6LHNTnByk88FNGblND_A1g3zxM42SCYpNgESMy-sunRGLYQArsmHj5yEcr2_IMN3UhIGIWcxtn_uj0lsCN_q3fBvmkLSBr8311mzGCNJ75DHa0bxIRQgG2gEt2GZd4hA1Is0/OhbysLe85gvx7cC15ZeEF33Syn3HvTit/7" target="_blank"&gt;重大&lt;/a&gt;看法。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;即将到来： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/F85eqdLzzUV0uzYWLpNs-nE_9F8tfZ3oGb05_W7M1a8bPU9BAe5BId1YXyfUAfoWCvq73f8kNn5WcJlt64OBz6ykZSWlJT3yCMhSUMPdmTwa1FO0XHR1I5u7OOoHwfwjqzOVvzZEyXSO78IQecVDXrGlVHJR8HACExK9ZdGQ0fqYdSNHniQR9t7B1P0X4dT0My57G7xa6pWZ4uNk3V65ppME47JOk9MRtZ78vfEWKWdP16vFhFAp_QTcTmvNGNhmj0a5961vI-3mBVO0b6AdaSB32Vk1_9WOeDB3VhVSc70HIJDajp_zRLnG8u_rSZ1yc3WAbnRiKK-paXCUn7Q7Raqt3a-DCyoBhB3VSG7RSeQHZnmOVZGjyvs0WgI/6KZetbvqWayxWBRQWk-B9OQbp__6sIuM/7" target="_blank"&gt;美国通货膨胀&lt;/a&gt;可能在三月份辞职， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eU4fnidlVY_t7paG0AhMOG2uvX9U7nwkTyC4zMcKnUc_B-vtEzrxJWxaFh6c4Z4hSkuBxFF1MXppgHbzvfa4anh9tog5MqecbsfEMtAsFsVTQQplOwDmOYaDwzerwHQVE6k_-cKP9nmWxgtwDqQIiaOzPd5PruFn6cio6FGLgQycfLtuj3pwfvmzZDPHloPWWWEcVwvfOT9lP9FjhyLIljxyU6YS8s0EJLr0cb_ze6KmqIkI47Fn5roOrn61zA2g0a4SknwSKnuKuCqzzgaFX2oe4ytAPodsPwVdoVQ-Ri-v1zlb9jxi21DivA8XHLvYFNKirCSCh0AYfeXNvabAE_gBxN8usiX_EULbojK7WxXl4isHbtwYJn7fUA8/ZFcvo2CYNDAKbLIpf4Rs-NcbTx2X7rxY/7" target="_blank"&gt;秘鲁&lt;/a&gt;可能会保持其利率不变。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt; “任何人的猜测”&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在特朗普对主要贸易伙伴的陡峭“互惠”关税计划之后，高盛经济学家周三对美国的“互惠”征收征收关税的计划&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/4GqA7VDGtL4Rwilj8NQ8ONGdBqX4Y6IXSrv8BMF-sSG7r5ZFiZ5t1bokum02_GkJ8hckoZp5eBZOcbS58QcK0LEvsGM0XDy09-uochl2yeAMijofjvBmnb9uK6etwaBXinLuuRizxGLmFtFdg2prZX5gPdQi3wIvXZmW_dLcz3RjyZ1YYMLlIAK_fXubUcnjItf7WLmKZe1KH41g0N9qAOpoosucxyDNQhzhGH5SF0woCib1ASOy491WKYJ9eRFgml_X8KjRk29Yt6Cv2KbV6jt1Fdusulru9Eez7Y_OnxpqY4FBGGA-K65RdE00HrT5RmZx11hJE4Z3erT3iZdEPcUC99DRvlhgOvK2QUcupvJXX8wV1yAI-ROkIIY/Zn3khivwpYsN3gRPZLJMsiAAQL3HAFes/7" target="_blank"&gt;加强&lt;/a&gt;了对美国的经济衰退风险估算的估计。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;中国104％的苏马省（后来升至125％）帮助Jan Hatzius及其同事提示了这一呼吁。该团队说：“白宫不太可能迅速扭转大多数新的关税，但如果这样做的话，我们的衰退可能性会下降。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;的确，没有迹象表明特朗普准备退缩&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/-OvL3dV_JZKjA97CsRz1zVDs6Lm_Y2rbHEQlMnODghR_5I85um-rcWMlYSzq0pszWtXL4Q7Qp7lyOWEfgOKBE2S5RfmH56-HoykkOdNsTyxgfFKmKy91nx3WGv97kEa_y71cIsKWM4oRFSIQ7iP5cZrHpmzqdjKq0YbzG7wjqRtHrbMhaWKEoKMC2GQPEC_TkX178DRxr7jGCa8Adyc0Drxpd_uHnXw25Z11Llpw6EBbxgx3UK1YNZd-9Xi6e14bgj2Yv7-214il8hCKw8uOywMQ8bCB59G3sT4nzvNCviPDZdLxeL4jGX8PB16CX66h1nZt5lfLdBjsp2dwQECvIwgnGUHIJ7euv7HjioY0q7uPYb5aPKJ0DSG7aqM/e6Lr45bNkmTYmgLq8ve_jNbiFIoLgXsh/7" target="_blank"&gt;互惠征税&lt;/a&gt;，他认为这是“善良”的，因为它们比政府对海外经济体对美国产品建造的一些真正保护水平的评估要小。周一，他明确&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AfyLRvjLcQDbJgUVK62Rr5iJOP-BMT0_UVzZ2-sxiQyD99f-4ZreI3mUbhLWPHQoG_Gjm1N1wdQIoVxWyi01tJxqJymXbAOtJyPt-I4NXdXOApuT2adyfkAPSKR5Kytlw5De9q8Azro--BmlYKNz0AXsbXPQtdU8JaLi5TS1vYlxJqdBZAjnfEpl54FBeS0dt2xav4nKsFnEGgYnh85Lmwcdw8mZeAL_lVVOshH6TCrYUZPUbYrdR7QrR-FAgKRP1DyrEqAXUHHGG1UCTFclujKU00xqzcL26p5dsQhS2oJeUlZ8LoF-CJSN9BKH2vd0hRHyOwYgIz0GhOzUed9zMoKb27Cr2p5kA2tWNR6FbJrhtqmTISfd_ZzPTyY/hijtZ9bET2mNohHHEZAKIfyT0c2U27Uo/7" target="_blank"&gt;否认猜测&lt;/a&gt;他可能会停下90天。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;但是他扭转了。高盛在公开时间超过一个小时之前&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/E7ZkyGHprWfB0pnLQX0gDNWfzcc-ba1Bh6UGVmhu0sIEdAArwPdYo-9y4VAzrmuinKAjv2krdLLj0aDnL1CGPrAZ02DgoRUUSwKU3fmLmhSCMJ3QW-A2d2_ohfxygOQzUTSvhgKGSYci8ejEmOBcjZnuJZR5rhBvCRnuzV_hCAenr8bKfYh0w-C3YQxRitrABiGBzwrL9UMpSoyLkftpi7B9Tk7RLYO9T25jUXYSVYfZ7BrfnjmSUNyMMSK8C4LzRlM9m0BFgl3Py5d1DIHEPBnx0n6Lv6IOEZKuOh5hETjaP6J8twjKWlP4Cb9HAnrJQR6nh6BluvkpEzXRQx00_TRnwIWE8WdhOwRnMwzdUAU3cikGsX1qQrsAwXo/6-Ur5ik2hT3WwEY6bkVAXzdepdzsNCUi/7" target="_blank"&gt;取消了经济衰退的电话&lt;/a&gt;。那是在特朗普宣布对任何被认为没有报复的国家的相互关税的90天停顿之后 - 截至周三截至周三的中国持有了125％的Surtax。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPLs2i0q7IMU/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPLs2i0q7IMU/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;里士满美联储总统汤姆·巴金。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：克里斯托弗·古德尼（Christopher Goodney）/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;里士满美联储（Richmond）总统汤姆·巴金（Tom Barkin）周三对听众说：“您知道方向是什么，您只是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lVgkUuuWo7lQUuOWS2g3dcwFAuigmXOzIqnQLOccb_1ucwgHgLkUom-ve-q1ofekZsAonJunVyYwD170NAXdV0zDsn8dVBJgdwf61LZmIdPvTw--qe56VK97KKt9F1b5ONhZNTs-mAn4bIiVco-IQ6DxNa0I1JoFLO65yG5kXNi6fY06GXwhNloTc49iS-pg8Tu9CtOTv_18dOLfTbDgJTHMFBhYRLsEFbqib4iwRxjRiAFIfyafPDVk3tOk80naPP8XcqF6ckb2duQbUuG2UL_7u0v4HBISwsjzu3LXGJWwPUd5pmHShJKYibmvQG48nhw3RFp_w4SmgtRWwoMgcc8tYeubiMcom6jW-A4qpOBoZ5i7U4-B7MYbQz0/t53pC-keZ0vi5ylZJ4RC0ZcEWAkuz_CQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;不知道目的地是什么&lt;/a&gt;。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;显然，征费将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/jbtE-_Xmj__tbWyMKDY4aHcIbHI9vCtYKDIn1Isi6TAuso4Dsn-6CGR3u47her9BZTOrPBnR2reMtflhJ2yr6hr4rzVdTP4-_FT3cwGY3iXgkt2BA-8F-vrPeW54gpGqB-SlgBk51ttsKWaEMoFe7sbjKX08bCESQ8onTLyCGErZ447nCvRG4dgKpaEPzPHox3hW4CRv50dMElHHMEKT4zOKNduvnnXP-Cno41seD0oNrC2COwC9zo-7Laqqp41TR3LihJ7qsW5soKmmMMU8YgVx3ghLnaxQbWzBP8ZqCEmuNaTrq2Rjp6ykMV32Kjbc-hLHYjTsUv2QSPp4jv0vCtaX7zvPOHp0sjVSeHW4z10m12J3lxULTCdi6aw/WIoLN07_5MGeuvMa70Pn5cVrAcgH_SYw/7" target="_blank"&gt;提高通货膨胀率&lt;/a&gt;（ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TARXzCzWXdSDJHY6S5n-MZdp27TdLKLxzsEUCdBTW8Xj1bIn-_2Dj9y-uloB-CHw8SX2AhPJsTiYWIv6X8JNfavwX_x0LwMwnWwt536PaJj4Sd9-k4VQ9qNKb0skemHPCKnhSXR_q-_IKDRTByG3cCviWWbD4QReG9hWVt4obzZSgYCemThy3Pil6GQtEJrJ-NE4ami_YD3tLnCErCs5ZNrgpXoJdLOJ9tqLZtM9H7fnJ9s_O2FoDIP0hnoZrBm4vtP0tgD97hXr1Odj2pR8OzEEsFRqx7zZ5wA8sTCoFp5WFwACpy0uwMyoCXmPQBp_pxMsKQ8C3cuu35dFrHgnz1R1Rr4DMWFgeOk5IVnHhkBTJB2IYNOUpFGKWYg/nK59QpITiGSHwXmDWKB5IV1ocLYgyRu-/7" target="_blank"&gt;最新的读数&lt;/a&gt;将于周四），2018  -  19年度特朗普第一届政府的关税也提高了对增长的“适度”损害。但这是较小的进口职责。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;巴金谈到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Y2lXhbXbfICVlMxCYbZZ20-m4Sc9ps8xnMDn492ceMnOxtkhcQg50XHKhnTIWk_g5Y81ADWQP_apsepAJK8UYqVZ5J493ZSVnQM6-8crHzy9GfrJOmc2wJUf91jDrcLX4GAcV-HIvF9NYNsxzRFozU05bk4l_P9836tYOrumYcIILrTmF7uoOqLLFbNPKTtdHyzGm9M9wuOoAqJSVsiBWL_kYHLqX6RfR4cIrGXUUNOnGHUtnnnbfCA4TttUke_hLfO0M4Uexzh4k4xrWTSpCnvqsuRNF0kVp0KjKmbMLQTwk2XxxJDa83zt-9MGDYVwjE1l7m0paijMd-UKS1QVMoAdihcmM_7xQfm8iYLHbDbV9hIjUGnlrVwBOYg/-yz7ffKnIUTHDEINxVIDnred-awi0mNj/7" target="_blank"&gt;关税的影响&lt;/a&gt;时说：“我认为这是任何人的猜测。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;从今年年初开始，尚不清楚特朗普是否真的在寻求交易交易，或者是新的更高水平的限制，迫使制造业重新升级给美国。接下来的几个月可能表明世界上最大的经济体正在前进。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;目前，财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）正在与&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pRhVnTBeEksoI0SsXAett-mwbG3QFNflsxvLe-8y2MHP3MtPmhnTMxHgZLojXzFKIwuP4GkOSwwaq--38bi2WJU9TBhJa1Lg-12MJgzxk-kebKV70v_t_g1lD_QnHx1W83aL5QUbYIzFSG311WOsRtfhuusjhoTzb7FAGooxwJmbolQv3Dy3vLbLWoUtuPtt3B6D_mQ4bdnA6FcCjSZCeZtmfObxyAHeK6574ssyePLmJKZl-c-haDSM9k4kn4qNjEJb43dQDEwGaWCc-EDjHrrlGPPsFaQcUr5HCX9REO3rUgzMWlGDkKudiZ0Aq8uGWh_442L4Yf4OkCQwfVbNIjGDGOvq9QOWUMiGts0NIe17OJHykJ23sNOmGwI/xUd7njoLM_n-ZgxdHirEyIQ849KZAOkM/7" target="_blank"&gt;盟友&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/L2PMD_F1WbOA_Bsc94um-w0O4nJ2_KOpwDrrrv-OrC7CTEMvakuhQHGyDQfE4Yofz8u-idThYJa_v0LuXhxRlB4mAb7AVnj5aBPKOZNxXfXnvR37VOSpFzhASr17d9q4CP--kEp80jpthpypszLF5UKtZQrbkHMWJyhdYLdvyl1E2INrFsB0qR4V1KIrZwSH5J-997OxqBcLs8yuwIUPEsqu-3SQpPMhPPW2JPFGSRYZ5jt6jdzht7HuE3ZHRusHJKWsJ2FS1ACHi2TymsLIRp6OrsLML6C5wLakSlPjXughG3BC0fQJ0re1epSM430IvEChfyxWjyl3R5tDjejcQzG3WSpPqYaGtd15MgxFssc08LlfYny34hrRQYI/xCLMXODVAtkFML1-E8vbfEaXo7qU2J0i/7" target="_blank"&gt;合作伙伴&lt;/a&gt;（包括围绕中国的那些地理位置上的伙伴）达成一系列交易，这将使世界其他地区具有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/DM_F2xWD760F6q2qb62An8FCCYAJmuaWITDbRE6ovWDKLEgX1zNqR_HrmordVCJ6MhEzGJjGZVe_ImIbK99_qrQ1ThdW3vmylKFCdDJiJ_Vk0kNZbkj5DJh_WDtFXbYAeIc8CSaBwkkhVdZSn35N1ljECT8WwjHg4dzIWgoag_xZT2ddPcI29MnZCtCc1Q3y06_csEgX0PFJNiARRRWUJpfQFIOkW-sRP0vIiuk3TL2PrrlwppvO54MckOiwAgKR_awL3-42mk7BdwcYA2Sxn6tmR1Gk0tjZ7099PfL9sr8-mEM8Hmq4xBwSlaycXIIih4eKg4aBFbfaBy4K_RxIbtX876XfhHgG9t04J0cMFmRinImefohfss7mg1Y/nXiJtzg6rNJEvDffYFJeqZ_hyecTYJlt/7" target="_blank"&gt;巨大的杠杆作用&lt;/a&gt;，以迫使北京降低其超能力并在全球贸易中获得更好的平衡。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;有关更多信息， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/87wZnBFZVYfPTNH7C4f-8HhlUVBSa0cGpylEEUGOXckSQAEP8tjYQcUw_Z0xObfVc3SiCP1w7csZLeZw1ZHKpVQ1OHN74tpO5IK9ue5fbww81H4af5FFhQ8vyVuIFENeCMImjW0ItDB8FEsiKBw4nmWDqFN