XyPZpCHNogqkTnkl1sC9vH25c2NcPMBqZGVXvkZiixT3CcRZTSXanFGyF61i0PpOgLpiiGXklYstGHIgeZF-aNU/_DjrJ3nPiSNZfJQqMGFiVbqYyews6Kwt/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOXN5AN.o69Q/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOXN5AN.o69Q/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Omersukrugoksu/Istockphoto&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;昨天对大多数投资者来说，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;市场很忙&lt;/strong&gt;，但对富人来说非常&lt;em&gt;非常&lt;/em&gt;好。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;世界上最富有的人&lt;/strong&gt;在周三的总净资产中增加了30040亿美元，这是彭博亿万富翁指数&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zoTeg4RwIxstrkuFtTu2KcrEAIMxCzotGAavw2AKP8ilTG2cluK6MM6rWcfHEomTHEGUPtiNwlEnrCaeEWoswfX0MowABjgRAdqQtm9trgZ8AiMyXZoESC-4Q8HnrVwWH0xOq2TWNUB6vS5Z1wQGY2SNNQ4sFzNuf-CcK_oeortaOfS3TfdzB8Kdlt-DBWIEaTO0caSegkKga6mN_JigJP-Cyr5n3mDu5lihy2SYvR0J368SOMifw21uvFN0Tbtz_2fCrvS49zuYtU948JP7BVMA8F050ERMdIeS8Q0SRI4UloMmKr6MIQWQhhx4MzO9ckZ7tf-Wa8SD5KfZfl-Nyomwnt21k-cRI4FBXgNsXTTEz1a7uvjlrZ8N2M0/-w8LBdtbSk7yWnk0G-9eiBnMNVDuJKe5/7" target="_blank"&gt;历史上最大的一日奖金&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;在特朗普决定停止一些关税之后，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;标准普尔500指数跃升了&lt;/strong&gt;2008年以来，这是最多的，这使世界500名最富有的人的命运平均提高了3.5％。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;甚至在市场周转之前，&lt;/strong&gt;一些亿万富翁购买了自己公司的股票，将较低的股价视为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/fLc0hHwAJZBogULuWHmeNFURVkKCJI-e76JCnTSF1VMDwExSxempHbs62zxzhWLaDrcpvqqANVqBewDQlU-mB50_tm9KuU8lQCk7bVcZyKxepSD7usuVmS3A1K2a1CnRJXRVBYK-IQNjQGbz_iODDnaD_Ri1VE_-_gdREZTljAr3pbbUVjOBb3T2WRVDvEiHCQNqHB7wFHXWMj_Kspf8ps-FJhEU7xoeek9GEP83eOS6owBzneDkk7KEc43tsVFAAstLgufDczezBYxGeAT_23IZJ3AKB0QQ2p9FasDmY5WJgkXJL1Us1gRjI_LrsZBc5udzt38gpNRaMMDn_KQRSWFAWhctpIcBBTWbATdiaA-5tSGqZtXoc8vsM2E/bcuz3IynafWwrhUrGZIyWsc3GtZonbVF/7" target="_blank"&gt;增加其股份的机会&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;如果您不富有，并且仍然吓坏了怎么办&lt;/strong&gt;？ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5QvmAEJuMotkJLEwobt3IZqpyqdoS3NQYW9WVWcjFAAc_FuXnIZSMpGcVFE6lH_ay7Xir3VXWPgzzLa70D9EilY1cqQATnbs-Ukyo3jAETLUvMGsNR6k1OVCNP4oZrxld44ceyE39067Zi0L2JCNhgmLB6J_w4gPiq1-VwBR1jZgdKDCiP7Kq6Lu9EhSSPHlG1w0kinAEX5wczO9RcOZoNEXaJXMOypQVNL0wLz7mJOz0bhBdl3EPkQzGtxBHeF9H1Gbn4SfMe1d8yRSw6WtgoTFhvyTLXvUI_NiRSGyhdw8T8dvqpIwjBW_Ii0KziAcNkR-1DWYoyutEvo-M836RxzrubwIvEm6VAKX7MvfI5e5Q2ipKZ5IHsK4Cio/TEYrm9lwOdNSuxQI3lAXVS_A7JAeY_YQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;要酷&lt;/a&gt;。这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/U_HxuSQ9usUTJkYqr30tW-_aJ4lbYAebGRjcxny5ppQpkISSFR4l1WtHmHi8GjkiBbEfxB5ByEEN3aj_eM0RKhARShOea7nUoifhQh_m9_gQnVdMuT-kOS2yr_Q6jwP9Xtp0TvFtelU0g7NSG8pJwi-4MbAD-Hm8XyCCsO57GSmkAE90NzzIj9T6_vgBeIGrGTaBEhTNW4f04dt3sp10WJHJaDrbg5zlTOJ4dOu6sZlvTyXzP3GbpcLafQxC5ssiII5IWwgDvrQf1JLn4armTaX7fyOalNZQoRu_56t72nfZ6YLp4yVbMWcW5GV_hmogwZMLVrbQU29YcN94DCAQ53RMIcW2tCSkC_76xTx1WTSZputFeDgkflsLhYY/LJGfcswCz1RqtteFXlz8k8TQtrFHCekj/7" target="_blank"&gt;您的投资组合“防衰退”的方法。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KPneG28ySfrG_K4LbeKtTTLvNIy2pCcp3IBxEPPS_ZlorFJ3jJ0yVCegJWndFpyeNuQyjjqvY2H6optE0oYfVoFrgQ26S31TFDz9cFBNYUfkDr1oskifvk0cZGe3ai2vUlW