sage.bloomberg.com/s/c/d3fEJqV-Sci9aykeTVhC6D1IG8ObA1fVstg2t1uHbGJKIHNWFvf2sHilwwNOQN2WJMs9ersG7gv80ExFwC3Czdx4dVUZ1LpOgAf15t5eDh1ntDMtEB2XFb_yBjfIrRqIFbvogfsKCkbyHfdYcZsbn5ChKzcbiDiNblz1xZMUi6TTVcHMw4gYzG2XeLr3xgnZ9neH_RD7XOIXcml3Qp6ltaeG_5XoD3udtEgHVDpGiYSGJQC1Z2T7dWEwJ39SBN5EcllLsnP2AphLCbEkgY7_PFTay3En0apHpn6pZhKweb3IJzA6gi-hHC6c8zsZEpqoYKcmIONXApV2V4Y0I8GvM_igf4wo_u8WL9bGYXEhow-8XvynIaSIVoiS6A/_8ZHC_AW8VEGMCTWwoUTn-lLm9plK-wC/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikjLrgdq29sI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikjLrgdq29sI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;截至目前，美国对钢铁，铝和汽车的关税仍处于目前的速度。除了北美贸易协定所涵盖的物品外，加拿大和墨西哥商品的关税对加拿大和墨西哥商品的关税也将保持不变。即使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/WgTLp9Brh5DHcff-LAsQqM4rduCQsFBdXb1tlwrUgtiLKllV6QYNmLE4uSZyKNWPAyK85rpoSefPRH-HSUFjLzUye0CG_a1KoajNBSLHCUmry2AyJ669vlomoec_XUak-8y37K4wduN9qRYNe8LCIvOGmVGoybH90nw5YA7YuS-zLu7MwwTyHYsnvJQCxiR5T3lWF2TOXRe8I78dz4tCnkQLa92WOU2mKcDqKunXc3DT5WMZGw8IDCjJbFhExgAeskKlrbKbSFct6d3QEooavEDhkPVCUUJfMiUTsVMGyD10pgpVYt9CDw7JxIfxbhl6YQrI0qHO7VKc1XpQZ9t7tbksAVP4qTUYOToMyZObAdoSyG0iurHiHu_oZgk/zWCFwpRqEgbf64sGYOsiHknuhqmw9bMe/7" target="_blank"&gt;集团宣布对金属关税进行报复&lt;/a&gt;，欧洲联盟即使税率仅面临10％的税。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;当特朗普的副官周三下午散发出突然的逆转时，独立的观察者将政府的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7fVw6q7L9EoF_N0jYC6EWW7Umu-7mIB9rGOpXR1iUOneVHeMquXxvm5bNBdOp4Ec0KFfEMdNr-rTLppfEgarcqr_OKtznDmxJQOzVp0J2lX_xSTIa2rQ0PUZO7oWY5D2Bafi_oBj1FeB1y