hy-trump-pause-tariffs-and-tariffs-and-and-what-what-happens-in-90-days&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/sbbwdXVYeOzi7yGqR7aLM8krnQEyMacA7RDm0-_SekYaLqJgDkpAW1-MwUXL9T6U-9q2WFMtW3cUCIeXfMWus6DlfOU2X5d7eZIq7zze79ZIlPY2MAuCbIjhjDsllFurAGfZ308a1m0IeiBq9gnx7tW0s8GqSSXBNXRYd1FOwNlKkOxZ-eSxCdAisqU6uDrDrzmGmYDyLE38qZbbudJkQJHZB_8aVCLEOTHz3KokuxrE1TlyT3eYhqIL4DZt2luIrasPyomTNjrpxOD6thtR0yj9wzQ0EK8bHmgc-p_i3HFkoVi1FLCQGUgq1sct5kCImWeYMvf0pCXNLPSYl_hRjrdZgfz9TQ_GimH3PBbASMVJzQ53k24HkODvUQk/Mv1D_PceXBk4PY7v32elC3F5blB4SdLa/7" target="_blank"&gt;？&lt;/a&gt;根据房屋股权投资公司Point的说法， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PP0ygSQNyLVMe1hlq1cUU1EsflJE87aBl_q5kn30ZI9zHmDUWOd_fAagTHV94xOygGIdVSeQ_VjIA8xZSgA78xoyg5y_DsyCMH4TfNOhRIi2Q5HAwkemmd1ncz64M4gVKQMwLFoTMMn6r7PbvVi8FSAbnXLtcMV9LJARwYUFTJ96PnTSN-TS5Q6cGgh_nKLuHTUgK76ytyjb6bV3k3U4wxsCmX7mtCpt8TFJY8Bcy7Wp1k5-NpiZ08JGGixjESjpCkA5wcEgdlJVdSFTFqcY7aAxLtqHPbTJEkni9IRxs0auDpBhsKllUxydn027P_fabh7TwuJNKhd5GwDOJ9QkCUevZtbWtjR5IJIHHbfMtrWSpWmDGWkbXIwm5Qw/wrFrQsIvaXcaF5ZF_5f5OFQ7jkhZgcI_/7" target="_blank"&gt;更高的利率和债务水平&lt;/a&gt;以及对工作和收入的流行性破坏使许多房地产贷款和信用额度更加困难。即使在过去几年的工作反弹之后，该研究发现，有抵押贷款的近460万房主经历了与信用评分较低有关的劳动力市场转变，这使他们获得了他们拥有超过7300亿美元的房屋股权的机会。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/8zM0rBSrYsEKnxpenueYUiFWYt0sWmDytbovik9-JYXNDbFElWD5Hqor5nK0rbWJ4EcEwi6eAZkgAVwu89dtIk7PGg1kADb51GeL__X0YB2sD8nzTacIQ2AJk45u9uPdsvCmv9YSlGZvOWeuOWlfSo8tNEQkIB0k8iIPvXkMtg-Cmc1V8i_mgK4rjoD304bmnfNhEim82geOvchlrT2UVI52ZgVHw6PqhrvTuQXzMdco1wtygoXWbhTJSP_YIskHfAT72uWFIqfAV2ujLGAR-JcGLqn1sdiP2h4bBuAAUR2G2KjQh6ifn3dbvJ0k212h6dv3TG1JufQA8DlQEYn70emRWzsh0N764pVeQNj_nwqTpug6RZ_NlEamShA/auEODreOgUQo-VPTO2RavclU4yRGcjU6/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i71R3uh_pB4w/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/